abstract: "Three field-verified Claude Code Skills extracted from 50+ rounds of cross-model independent review across 5 LLM backends: session-end (session handoff), write-claude-md (CLAUDE.md authoring), and kill-test-first (pre-registration decision audit). Each skill follows a unified router-pattern design with progressive disclosure and was independently validated through adversarial multi-backend review."
